---
title: Bison and Bacon Cheeseburgers with Steak-Spiced Potato Wedges
description: This bacon cheeseburger is truly epic. Tonight, bison comes in for the win! It's lean, flavourful and pairs perfectly with rich and smoky bacon. To gild the lily, we've added melty white cheddar and zesty mayo.
